{"tid":2055680,"cid":31,"subCid":0,"title":"天文台特別提示：短期內廣泛地區大雨 料80公里強風襲港","createTime":"2020-06-08T06:49:22.000Z","updateTime":"2020-06-08T07:23:06.000Z","uid":71166,"like":7,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":5,"replies":[{"pid":"ff9880f80a4f940571ce17c8209fc2bc7599700f","tid":2055680,"uid":71166,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-08T06:49:22.000Z","msg":"天文台下午1時15分發出「特別天氣提示」，指短期內香港廣泛地區可能受大雨影響，市民應提高警覺。 <br />\n<br />\n天文台先於中午12時10分指，短期內香港廣泛地區可能受大雨影響，市民應提高警覺。到12時20分，天文台預料高達每小時80公里或以上的強陣風吹襲香港。<br />\n<br />\n一道低壓槽正為廣東沿岸帶來雷雨。天文台今早8時55分曾發出黃雨警告，警告至上午11時15分取消。本港今早多處地區錄得約20毫米雨量，而大埔及荃灣的雨量更超過50毫米。<br />\n<br />\n建立時間：12:21<br />\n<br />\n更新時間：13:18<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://s.yimg.com/ny/api/res/1.2/WBE7O4QdDKda.mAoTrcHKw--~A/YXBwaWQ9aGlnaGxhbmRlcjtzbT0xO3c9ODAwO2lsPXBsYW5l/http://media.zenfs.com/en_us/News/singtao/20200608a130533.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fs.yimg.com%2Fny%2Fapi%2Fres%2F1.2%2FWBE7O4QdDKda.mAoTrcHKw--~A%2FYXBwaWQ9aGlnaGxhbmRlcjtzbT0xO3c9ODAwO2lsPXBsYW5l%2Fhttp%3A%2F%2Fmedia.zenfs.com%2Fen_us%2FNews%2Fsingtao%2F20200608a130533.jpg&h=0755e73e&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"76a5bec8edc61344ff07497123f9ac89493f130c","tid":2055680,"uid":84081,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-06-08T06:50:20.000Z","msg":"1點15分既野依家先講做乜<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/give.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b6ad584c6c2ce4740bbe02854982fae257c857fb","tid":2055680,"uid":71166,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"76a5bec8edc61344ff07497123f9ac89493f130c","tid":2055680,"uid":84081,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-06-08T06:50:20.000Z","msg":"1點15分既野依家先講做乜<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/give.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-08T06:51:36.000Z","msg":"天文台先於中午12時10分指，短期內香港廣泛地區可能受大雨影響<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/smi